shlog
=====
a blog in /bin/sh.  
this project is a work in progress.

depends
-------
* /bin/sh  
* lowdown  

config
------
the config file is located at `${XDG_CONFIG_HOME}/shlog/shlog.conf`.  
a default config is included as `shlog.conf.def`.

